Ak se neko muci sa plotanjem : 

ja sam to napravio u 3d-u u matlabu, sad neznam jel to tako treba : 

```
dio1 = importdata('poze_point.txt');
Spill=dio1.data;
dio2 = importdata('poze_taylor.txt');
Spill2=dio2.data;

X = Spill(:,1);
Y = Spill(:,2);
Z = Spill(:,3);

plot3(X,Y,Z,'r')
xlabel('X[m]');
ylabel('Y[m]');
zlabel('Z[m]');

hold on

X2 = Spill2(:,1);
Y2 = Spill2(:,2);
Z2 = Spill2(:,3);

plot3(X2,Y2,Z2,'b')

hold on

X3 = matrica(:,1);
Y3 = matrica(:,2);
Z3 = matrica(:,3);

plot3(X3,Y3,Z3,'g')

grid on


```

